# 💼 Personal Developer Portfolio

Welcome to my personal developer portfolio! Built using modern web technologies to showcase my skills, projects, and experience as a full-stack developer.

![Portfolio Screenshot](./public/preview.png) <!-- Replace with actual screenshot if available -->

---

## 🔗 Live Demo

[Visit My Portfolio](https://your-portfolio.vercel.app/) <!-- Replace with actual URL once deployed -->

---

## 🚀 Tech Stack

- ⚛️ React 19 (Vite)
- 🎨 Tailwind CSS
- 🎬 Framer Motion
- 🖊️ React-Typical (Typewriter effect)
- 🔧 Node.js (for backend API if added)
- 🧠 Deployed via Vercel/Netlify

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```bash
portfolio/
├── public/               # Static assets
├── src/
│   ├── components/       # Reusable components
│   ├── pages/            # Main pages (About, Projects, Contact)
│   ├── App.jsx           # App root
│   ├── main.jsx          # Entry point
├── .gitignore
├── package.json
└── vite.config.js

🧪 Installation & Setup
Clone the repo

bash
git clone https://github.com/ismailcodes-dev/portfolio.git
cd portfolio

Install dependencies
bash
npm install

Run the dev server
bash
npm run dev
Visit http://localhost:5173 in your browser.

✨ Features
Responsive and clean design

Smooth page transitions and animations

Typing effect for hero section

Projects with GitHub & live demo links

Contact form (can integrate with EmailJS or Formspree)

Mobile-friendly